{
  "stem": "27748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the living arrangements were that-- I mean, it was co-educational.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived separately.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was one main house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where the girls lived, and the staff, I believe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not clear where the staff lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lived in the adjacent buildings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the-- what I should also emphasize is there were two locations, two places for Bunce Court.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were in Bunce Court in Kent for about two years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when there was the threat of invasion, of German invasion, the whole school was moved to Shropshire, just east of Wales to-- in the country, to sort of a country estate.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the living arrangements-- sometime I get them mixed up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, the boys and girls lived separately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we worked together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In Shropshire, for instance, I know we were-- the boys were living in converted stables, horse stables.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the girls lived in the main building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we-- it was a very much a community, and with emphasis on equality.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We called the teachers by their first name, which in those days was, perhaps, unheard of.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But food-- I was not brought up on food, or putting much-- I don't remember what we ate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't remember much emphasis on cooking, although we helped out in the kitchen, the children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I don't recall anything about particular foods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But that was part of my upbringing, that food was not a big thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was very non-religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was borderline between non-religious and anti-religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no commitment to practicing Judaism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From the headmistress on down, these people were not practicing orthodox, or even conservative, Judaism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when it came time for me to be bar mitzvah, several of us were bar mitzvahed together.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
